---
layout: layout-base.njk
title: Blog
description: Praxiswissen rund um Fotobox-Vermietung für Firmenevents in D · LUX — Preisvergleiche, Eventberichte, Tipps für Buchung und Planung.
permalink: /blog/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:900px">

    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p class="section__lead">
      Praxiswissen aus 14 Jahren Fotobox-Vermietung im Saarland und darüber hinaus —
      Preisvergleiche, Eventberichte, Tipps für die Buchung Ihres Firmenevents.
    </p>

    {% set posts = collections.post | reverse %}

    {% if posts | length == 0 %}
      <p style="color:var(--grey);padding:2rem;background:var(--light);border-radius:var(--radius);text-align:center">
        Erster Beitrag erscheint in Kürze.
      </p>
    {% else %}
      <div class="blog-list" style="margin-top:2rem">
        {% for post in posts %}
          <article class="blog-list__item card"
                   style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding:1.75rem;border:1px solid var(--light)">

            {% if post.data.topic %}
              <p style="color:var(--red);font-weight:900;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin:0">
                {{ post.data.topic }}
              </p>
            {% endif %}

            <h2 style="margin:0.25rem 0 0.5rem;font-size:1.5rem">
              <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color:var(--dark);text-decoration:none">
                {{ post.data.title }}
              </a>
            </h2>

            <p style="color:var(--grey);font-size:0.9rem;margin:0 0 0.75rem">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | dateDe }}</time>
              {% if post.data.readingTime %} · {{ post.data.readingTime }} Min. Lesezeit{% endif %}
            </p>

            {% if post.data.excerpt %}
              <p style="margin:0 0 1rem">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
            {% endif %}

            <p style="margin:0">
              <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color:var(--red);font-weight:700">
                Weiterlesen →
              </a>
            </p>

          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <p style="margin-top:3rem;color:var(--grey);font-size:0.9rem">
      RSS-Feed: <a href="/feed.xml">/feed.xml</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>
